<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٤٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>﴿فَأْتُوهُنَّ مِنْ حَيْثُ أَمَرَكُمُ <span class="c2">(اللَّهُ)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>﴾ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(تعتزلوهن)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> في المحيض.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
